snippet.textDisplay:
This is not so much a car, more a massive list of luxury items on 4 wheels.
I like that it is not covered in gold and blingy, although excessive in many other ways.
If you are driving to your super yaught and you want to turn up in style, this is probably the car, but I think Rolls Royce need to start thinking about the environment and doing all of this in a more sustainable way.
